OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Campaigners are taking the government  
OL,6, to court accusing it of failing to stop
OL,7, chicken manure polluting the River Wye.
OL,9,FThe case has been brought by the       
OL,10,Fcharity River Action which says laws   
OL,11,Fdesigned to keep waterways healthy have
OL,12,Fnot been enforced.                     
OL,14,FThe Wye last year had its status       
OL,15,Fdowngraded to "unfavourable" with some 
OL,16,Fblaming the rapid expansion of chicken 
OL,17,Ffarming in the catchment area.         
OL,19,FThe Environment Agency said anyone     
OL,20,Fbreaking the law could be prosecuted.  
